{
  "stem": "151.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a mother and daughter by the name of Farkosh.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't know what happened to them after that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Farkosh, the mother, in the morning saw that I can't stand on my feet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So she stole somewhere a blanket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know where and how.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she wrapped me in this blanket, and she dragged me out for zahlappell.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Would she have not done it, I would have been finished that morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She dragged me out, and I went through the shower and the icy water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then I went on this death march, about 60 kilometers, where we were again put into cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then this cattle car, my prisoner friends surrounded me, and hugged me for body warmth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I arrived to the next camp, to Liebau, totally recovered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The icy water brought my temperature down, and it was just a miracle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think that's the way to cure sore throat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Liebau, I don't even know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't very far, because Liebau was in Upper Silesia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I know that the journey lasted, again, three days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what was this three day journey that they invented, that everything lasted three days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was out of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- you know, I was sick, and I had temperature, and I really was worried that I'm not going to make it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we arrived, and I realized that I can walk-- I can stand up, I can walk-- they unloaded us at the railroad station, and we walked through this little town where they never saw a Jew before.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we later were assigned to work at a Krupp factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this group, there was about 200 of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
